definitions.definition: ( zoology ) Sexual desire in any of many mammals , often specific to mating season . [from early 15th c.]
The noise made by deer during sexual excitement.
Roaring , as of waves breaking upon the shore; rote .
( fandom slang , countable , uncountable ) In omegaverse fiction, the intense biological urge of an alpha to mate , typically triggered by proximity to an omega in heat .

definitions.definition: A furrow , groove , or track worn in the ground, as from the passage of many wheels along a road.
A fixed routine , procedure, line of conduct, thought or feeling.

examples: Dull job, no interests, no dates. He's really in a rut .
